OL,3,CNext government needs plan for growth
OL,4,Cwithin 100 days, says CBI
OL,6,FThe next UK government must develop a
OL,7,Fcredible plan for sustainable economic
OL,8,Fgrowth and draw investment within its
OL,9,Ffirst 100 days, according to a leading
OL,10,Fbusiness group.
OL,12,FThe Confederation of British Industry
OL,13,F(CBI) has called for an immediate
OL,14,Ffocus on the economy following the
OL,15,FGeneral Election in July, after a
OL,16,Fturbulent few years for UK businesses.
