OL,3,CNext government needs plan for growth
OL,4,Cwithin 100 days, says CBI
OL,6,FIt comes amid a backdrop of sharply-
OL,7,Fincreased interest rates ` which sit
OL,8,Fat a 16-year-high of 5.25% ` and shaky
OL,9,Fconsumer sentiment following soaring
OL,10,Finflation over the past two years.
OL,12,FThe CBI has said the next government
OL,13,Fmust "revitalise brand Britain" in a
OL,14,Fbid to attract further investment into
OL,15,Fthe country.
