OL,3,CNext government needs plan for growth
OL,4,Cwithin 100 days, says CBI
OL,6,FThe trade group said in its pre-
OL,7,Felection "business manifesto" that
OL,8,Ffirms want to see a cutting-edge trade
OL,9,Fand investment strategy from the next
OL,10,Fgovernment, in order to grow UK
OL,11,Fexports, secure imports and improve
OL,12,Finvestment.
OL,14,FRain Newton-Smith, chief executive
OL,15,Fofficer of the CBI, said: "Top of the
OL,16,Fin-tray should be sharpening the
OL,17,Finvestor pitch for 'brand Britain' `
OL,18,Fensuring we are at the very top of the
OL,19,Fleague table when it comes to
OL,20,Finvestment.
