OL,3,CNext government needs plan for growth
OL,4,Cwithin 100 days, says CBI
OL,6,F"At the same time, a focus on building
OL,7,Fmomentum behind the 'big three'
OL,8,Fenablers across tax, planning and the
OL,9,Flabour market within the first 100
OL,10,Fdays can give firms a clear flightpath
OL,11,Ffor growth.
OL,13,F"We want to see a new government
OL,14,Fdeliver a bold pitch to investors
OL,15,Facross the globe, restore the UK's
OL,16,Fcompetitiveness and double down on our
OL,17,Fclimate commitments and opportunities."
