OL,3,CNext government needs plan for growth
OL,4,Cwithin 100 days, says CBI
OL,6,FIt also urged the General Election
OL,7,Fwinner to deliver a net zero
OL,8,Finvestment plan to help create more
OL,9,Fjobs linked to energy security and
OL,10,Fefficiency.
OL,12,FThe CBI also highlighted a need to
OL,13,F"unlock the power of UK regions" and
OL,14,Falign a future industrial and trade
OL,15,Fstrategy with regional UK mayors.
