OL,3,CNext government needs plan for growth
OL,4,Cwithin 100 days, says CBI
OL,6,FMs Newton-Smith added: "The UK economy
OL,7,Fhas spent the last five years buffeted
OL,8,Fby a series of 'one-off' shocks ` from
OL,9,Fthe aftermath of Brexit, to Covid, to
OL,10,Fglobal conflict and the subsequent
OL,11,Fenergy crisis.
OL,13,F"As a result, our economy has
OL,14,Funderstandably focused more on shock
OL,15,Fabsorption than on boosting growth.
OL,17,F"A new government of whatever colour
OL,18,Fprovides an opportunity to shift gear
OL,19,Fand prioritise the long-term decisions
OL,20,Fthat can deliver a decade of
OL,21,Fsustainable growth."
